WEBVTT

00:00:03.274 --> 00:00:06.735 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
There are millions of Jehovah’s Witnesses
around the world,

00:00:09.363 --> 00:00:11.615 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
each finding a way

00:00:11.615 --> 00:00:13.284 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
to be joyful.

00:00:15.744 --> 00:00:17.872 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Despite the trials we face,

00:00:17.872 --> 00:00:20.708 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
we can find joy

00:00:20.708 --> 00:00:23.085 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the choices we’re making, 

00:00:26.547 --> 00:00:28.924 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the families we’re raising, 

00:00:31.302 --> 00:00:33.345 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the creation we’re observing, 

00:00:40.477 --> 00:00:43.314 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
from the peace we’re promoting.

00:00:44.815 --> 00:00:46.442 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Joy is found

00:00:46.442 --> 00:00:48.861 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
in the message we’re preaching.

00:00:52.990 --> 00:00:55.993 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah promises us joy despite 

00:00:55.993 --> 00:00:58.495 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
the trials we’re enduring

00:00:58.495 --> 00:01:01.040 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
and persecution we’re facing.

00:01:01.040 --> 00:01:03.000 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He promises us joy

00:01:03.000 --> 00:01:05.669 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
through the stand we’re taking.

00:01:06.795 --> 00:01:08.881 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Through anything in life,

00:01:08.881 --> 00:01:11.467 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
you can find joy in Jehovah.

00:01:12.134 --> 00:01:14.136 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
He wants you to be happy.

00:01:15.846 --> 00:01:17.848 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
His joy can be yours

00:01:17.848 --> 00:01:19.683 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
now and forever!

00:01:21.352 --> 00:01:24.813 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
So will you accept it?

